nodes.text: The Tatooine Dash was a secret hyperspace route used by the Desilijic kajidic to decrease the travel time between Hutt Space and its important Tatooine holdings.

The Tatooine Dash began at Nar Kaaga, passed through the Manda system, and ended at Tatooine. It intersected the Kaaga Run at Nar Kaaga, the Manda Merchant Route and the Manda-Roon Merchant Route at Manda, and the Corellian Skip Run, the Crystal Passage, the Old Corellian Run and the Triellus Trade Route at Tatooine.
